<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天是感恩节放假的前一天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜很感谢，因为老师没有布置作业！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>儿童中心里，莉琪戴着一个印第安头饰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是她在美术课上做的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我感谢印第安人让我们吃到玉米。我喜欢玉米。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36975</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她蹦蹦跳跳，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！我还感谢漂亮的花！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师手里拿着两大花瓶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些花是活动用的吗？” 尼娜问。她希望是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56142</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“秋天结束意味着鲜花也不开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要压这些花，然后等它们干。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个星期以后，我们就可以用这些压花了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要怎么用呢？” 尼娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77888</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可以用它们做卡片。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我带了一些上个月压好的花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们压好花以后，要做感谢卡。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“感恩节的感谢卡吗？” 波比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。” 雪莉老师回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“做压花的时候，想想要感谢的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，选四朵花吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜看着橙色、黄色和红色的花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他人都拿好了花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，每一朵花都很美，太难选了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尼娜，你选好了吗？” 雪莉老师在等她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜闭上眼睛，选出四朵花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，雪莉老师告诉大家怎么做压花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拿一张纸对折。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把纸打开，把花放进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不要让花碰到一起。然后盖起来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156874</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真可爱，像一本小小的花书。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156874</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163475</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在拿一本大词典。” 雪莉老师拿起一本词典，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“词典会帮我们压花。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“翻到词典最后一页。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175879</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把小花书放在最后一页和封皮之间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175879</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过几个星期，就有漂亮的压花了。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜按照雪莉老师的话做了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜希望自己的压花会很漂亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“想到要感谢的人了吗？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她打开一个红色盒子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201066</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿出一叠纸板。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜看到纸板里有几张压花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师给了他们空白的卡片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“写完卡片，在上面涂胶水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后选一些压花，轻轻放上去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个星期后，你们今天做的压花也会变干。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到时你们可以在家里做这样的卡片。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜看着雪莉老师。“您的感谢卡是给谁的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师沉默了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的妈妈。” 她说，“你呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜害羞地笑了。“这是秘密。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“该回家了！尼娜，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>别忘了你的卡片。” 雪莉老师叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是写给您的。” 尼娜告诉老师，“再见！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师打开卡片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上面写着：“亲爱的雪莉老师，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢谢您在儿童中心给我们带来238天的欢乐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>感恩节快乐！——尼娜”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>